Login and SignUp project with Firebase
----login-Page
----signUp-Page
----dashboard-Page

I copy a pre-built Login and SignUp form from W3 school .
The Loginpage appear first, then a button at the bellow to signUp if the user have not,
The signUp form contain
--Fullname
--Email address
--password
--confirmPassword
--checked button
After successfully enterd the requested data it check if the password match the confirmpassword that is inputed.
Then Firebase create user with EmailAndPassword inputted and save.
--If password doest not match firebase or sweetAlert will send an erro message
--But if confirm to matches it sweeAlert send a success message
    Firebase --- createUserWithEmailAndPassword in signUp form
Login form
Login form contain email and password
Once email and password is inputed and submitted firebase check user has account with them 
--If yes it, it send a success alert using sweeAlert
--If no, an error message will be send by firebase or sweetAlert
    Firebase --- signInWithEmailAndPassword in login form
Dashboard has nothing much, it was created to direct user to the main page


Technology Used:
---Javascript
---Firebase
---sweeAlert
